<L>__{exterior mountain country night}
<A>__{the stage is now heading uphill, the gentle slope at the beginning of the foothills.}
<L>__{exterior mountain country night}
<A>__{the road is steeper now, and winding. another angle. the road is cut out of the side of the mountain, leaving a sheer slope on one side, and high, thick trees and brush on the other. as the stage follows a bend in the road, a rider leaps out and grabs the lead horse. the stage lurches crazily and almost overturns as it slows to a stop. before haven can free his hands from the reins to go for his gun, two shadowy figures, handkerchiefs helping the darkness mask their faces, have jumped out onto the road ahead and have him covered.}
