<C>__{second bandit's voice}
<D>__{that's far enough.}
<A>__{the footsteps halt. mick aims and fires. by wagon. there is a half grunt, half groan from goddard. haven turns as if to protest and then crumples as a gun fells him. close shot haven, lying face down on the ground, unconscious.}
